        "content": "<p>Welcome <span aria-label=\"wave\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44b\" role=\"img\" title=\"wave\">:wave:</span> You can state this more abstractly as the existence of an equivalence betwen <code>Fin N × Fin M</code> and <code>Fin (N * M)</code>, which in mathlib is <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=finProdFinEquiv#doc\">docs#finProdFinEquiv</a></p>",
